\c 8
\s Nowa anobuda muareka
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mwari wakarangarira Nowa nechose chinorarama, nechipfuwo chose chaiva naye muareka. Mwari akafambisa mhepo panyika, mvura ndokuserera.
\v 2 Zvini kwakadzivirwa zvitubu zvepakadzika nemahwindo ematenga akadzivirwa, nemvura yakabva kudenga ikadziviswa.
\v 3 Mvura ndokuramba ichidzoka achibva panyika, mvura ndokuderera shure kwemazuva zana nemakumi mashanu.
\v 4 Zvino areka yakagara mumwedzi wechino­mwe, nezuva regumi nemanomwe re­mwedzi pamusoro pama­komo eArarati.
\v 5 Mvura ndokuramba ichiderera kusvikira pamwedzi wegumi; nemwedzi wegumi, nezuva rekutanga remwedzi kwakaonekwa misoro yemakomo.
\p
\v 6 Zvino zvikaitika pakupera kwemazuva makumi mana, kuti Nowa akazarura hwindo reareka raakanga aita,
\v 7 akabudisa gunguvo, iro rikaramba richiyengerera ku­svikira mvura yapwa panyika.
\v 8 Akatumawo njiva kubva paaiva, kuti aone kana mvura yaserera pachiso chenyika;
\v 9 asi njiva haina kuwana zororo rerutsoka rwayo, ikadzokera kwaari kuareka, ne­kuti mvura yaiva pamusoro pechiso chenyika yose; akatambanudza ruoko rwake, akai­tora, akaipinza kwaari muareka.
\v 10 Zvino wakagara amwe mazuva manomwezve; akatuma njiva muareka.
\v 11 Njiva ikapinda kwaari madekwani, zvino tarira, mumuromo mayo maiva neshizha remuorivhi rakatanhwa; naizvozvo Nowa wakaziva kuti mvura yaiva yaserera kubva panyika.
\v 12 Zvino wakagara amwe mazuva manomwe, akatuma njiva; iyo haina kudzokerazve kwaari zvekare.
\p
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika mgore remazana matanhatu nerimwe, pamwedzi wekutanga, nemusi wekutanga wemwedzi, mvura yaiva ya­pwa kubva panyika; zvino Nowa wakabvisa denga reareka, akaona, zvino tarira, pasi pose paoma.
\v 14 Zvino nemwedzi wechipiri, nezuva rema­kumi maviri nemanomwe remwedzi, nyika yaiva yaoma.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Mwari wakataura naNowa achiti:
\v 16 Buda muareka, iwe, nemukadzi wako, nevanakomana vako, nevakadzi vevanakomana vako pamwe newe.
\v 17 Chose chinorarama chinewe, panyama yose, yeshiri neyechipfuwo neyechose chinokambaira, chinokambaira panyika, buda nacho; kuti chibereke chiwande panyika chibereke chiwande pamusoro penyika.
\v 18 Zvino Nowa wakabuda, iye nevanakomana vake, nemukadzi wake, neva­kadzi vevanakomana vake pamwe naye.
\v 19 mhuka yose, nechinokambaira chose, neshiri yose, nechipi nechipi chinokambaira panyika, nemarudzi azvo, zvakabuda paareka.
\v 20 Zvino Nowa wakavakira Je­hovha aritari, akatora pamhuka dzose dzakanaka neshiri dzose dzaka­naka, akapisira zvipiriso zvinopiswa paa­tari.
\v 21 Jehovha akanzwa kunhuhwira kwa­kanaka, Jehovha akati mumoyo make: Handichapi nyika rushambwazve nekuda kwemunhu; nekuti kufunga kwemoyo we­munhu kwakaipa kubva pauduku hwake; uye handichazorovizve chipenyu chose.
\v 22 Nguva yose yenyika, ku­dzvara nekukohwa, kutonhora nekudziya, zhizha nechando, masikati neusiku hazvi­ngagumi.
